---
description: Best practices for using Mantine UI components and styling
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx,css}
---
- Use Mantine's theme system for consistent styling
- Implement form validation with `@mantine/form`
- Utilize `@mantine/hooks` for custom hooks and state management
- Use `@mantine/notifications` for user feedback
- Implement date pickers with `@mantine/dates`
- Use `@mantine/dropzone` for file uploads